{"type": "article", "id": 21049, "title": "灵感来自巧克力棒的瓷砖", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-21T07:24:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122313VMFyuItWhJivmgnT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组墙饰来自西班牙的 MUT Design，灵感源于巧克力棒。它有灰、白、橙三种颜色，在瓷砖表面形成略有厚度的网格纹路，有的是整齐的方形，有的穿插以长方形或空白，可以形成一种几何感。一些地方的是密集的，一些地方显得稀疏，可以垂直或倾斜排列，但整体风格是纯粹的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150733utaMIeXcoAj0YrlV.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1403\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150733BzpOVbewIYG5tDoC.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"668\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150734k7rAgTQpj9HOtuyq.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1403\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150734dkcHv9il2QgqI3Ob.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}